--<{7/17/24 patch}>--
--Remade Animation, added torso movement and arm is now attached to Rootpart
--These Settings Are Very Loosely Locked, Put In 'nil' For Default Stuff, And you can set value as long as it matches the required type

--<<Settings>>--
local AnimType: ('Smooth' | 'Realistic' | 'Random') = 'Random'
local TorsoMovement: boolean? = true
